    public class SlovakIDCombinedRecognitionResult
extends BaseRecognitionResult
implements CombinedRecognitionResult
    Represents a result of scanning of both front and back side of Slovak national ID card.

      • isDocumentDataMatch

        public boolean isDocumentDataMatch()
        Returns true if both data on the front side of the document and on the back side of the document match, false otherwise. Address, place of birth, surname at birth, special remarks are present only at back side and issued by, date of issue and personal number are only at front side, all other data elements are present on both sides and their values are matched.
        Specified by:
        isDocumentDataMatch in interface CombinedRecognitionResult
        Returns:
        true if both front and back side data match, false otherwise.
